- Add an /etc/bu/bu.conf file with a list of directories to either not backup,
  or to backup to an alternate backup dir name.

    [backup_dirs]
    #
    # Path                            [BackupDir or DONT_BACKUP]
    #
    /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts    BACKUPS


  Also include a directive to specify the default backup directory name.

    BackupDir = .bu_backups


- detect special files and handle them via tarball
- handle files with single quotes in the file name


